<p>In <a href="https://archive.org/details/twomovechessprob0000moor/page/154/mode/2up?view=theater"><em>Two-Move Chess Problems</em></a> (1986), Robert Moore calls this a &#8220;very lightweight jewel.&#8221; White to mate in two moves.</p>

