<p>1. Re2!, waiting:</p>
<p>1. &#8230; d5 2. Re6#<br />
1. &#8230; Kb5 2. Rc2#<br />
1. &#8230; Kd5 2. Bg2#</p>
<p>By Otto Wurzburg, from the <em>Grand Rapids Herald</em>, 1932.</p>
